node.text:
Targeting your quads 🦵is a struggle without gym equipment 🤦‍♀️ but I found a few workouts that really set them on fire 🔥 ! Add these to your leg day! Wanted to share this workout here so it’s easier to find! Stay motivated babes!!! We got this!💘💪
Weights are from Costco came in a set with weights from 10lbs to 30lbs with a rack for only $230 🤯! In store only!

node.text: We are home 🙌🏻! What a fun trip 💕! Giving all the details on stories tomorrow tips and things I wish I would have known before going 😂! Walked a total of 30 miles in the three days and I’m sore in places I didn’t know I could be!😱! Such a cool place though loved seeing the kids faces light up ❤️!

node.text:
Day two of our first family trip to Disneyland 🎢 and our favorite ride so far has been The Millenium Falcon ride in Star Wars Land and our favorite at California Adventure was Cars! We have officially walked a million miles 🤣🤣 and had so many treats it’s unreal! I would highly recommend (if you have Star Wars fans like my boys) building a droid at Droid Depot! My boys will definitely remember that forever! They seriously go above and beyond here ❤️!
